Here is SQL queries with common table expression for film lengths:

Average film length:

	SELECT AVG(length)								
	FROM film		
  
Titles of the longest films (Length=185):

	SELECT film_id,								
	title,								
	length								
	FROM film								
	ORDER BY length DESC
  
Titles of the shortest films (Length=46):

	SELECT film_id,								
	title,								
	length								
	FROM film								
	ORDER BY length ASC								
